description: City: Boca Raton, FLTikiz Shaved Ice serves delicious desserts to the streets of Boca Raton. The “Tikiz” product line combines two of the most popular mainstream frozen treat products that everyone loves, Ice Cream and refreshing Hawaiian Shaved Ice. All shaved ice cups come with a gumball in the bottom. Choose your own flavor or mix many on the Surv-Board. Tikiz also offers sugar-free  & other syrup options as well. Cool down with Tikiz Shaved ice today!
name: Tikiz Shaved Ice
